Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:18.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's our tentative program.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:19.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:21.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,The mission starts-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:24.40,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going out, Kana-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.82,0:02:28.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.65,0:02:31.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,She must be going off to spend her first salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:32.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Not all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:37.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sending some back home, and I thought of sending a present along with it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.14,0:02:39.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,A reward for yourself, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.49,0:02:41.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:46.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,You were just a trainee for the first month, and didn't get paid, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.44,0:02:47.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:48.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.43,0:02:49.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:53.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that it was common for the salary to be delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:55.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's normally paid in military scrip.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:58.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Thank you for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:02.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:08.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that I would actually get paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.16,0:03:10.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Because for that, our unit has a side-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:17.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata... err... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:19.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a market in town today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your first time seeing one, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:23.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Your first salary and first day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.20,0:03:26.13,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a variety of 'firsts' for Kana-chan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:29.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave the job behind, and enjoy yourself thoroughly. {lit: Forget the job, and just spread out your wings.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.72,0:03:30.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.10,0:03:36.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata's Day Off - Hair Braiding
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.35,0:03:40.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:52.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you not to spill that to Kanata, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:55.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if she were to just use common sense...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.00,0:03:59.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,In such a remote region as this, not to mention the delay, they wouldn't even send salary, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.25,0:04:08.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, Kanata believed it so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:11.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Honesty is one of Kana-chan's better traits.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.79,0:04:12.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:16.19,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to start spending her money almost immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:18.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the two of you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.06,0:04:19.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.14,0:04:25.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:29.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,...shall we forget our main jobs too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:38.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:39.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:42.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, there is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:44.89,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no further discounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.96,0:04:52.90,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I was in a daze, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.38,0:05:06.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.24,0:05:06.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,No problems at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.46,0:05:12.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, a problem has just come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:16.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding that, I do have a suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.61,0:05:17.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you take it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:20.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please tell us the details?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.49,0:05:22.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.48,0:05:27.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cute, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.81,0:05:46.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:49.22,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,...the sellers of these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:05:59.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it that they are to your liking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.44,0:06:00.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Not too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:06.47,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's a slight problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:08.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what would that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:10.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,With so few goods,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be more work than it's worth just to sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.84,0:06:18.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think of it that way, it doesn't really cover my expenses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.03,0:06:18.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:21.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my policy to give discounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.85,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,The worth is in its flavor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:27.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't say that I have lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:32.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:33.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even try!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:41.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're gonna shoot, then shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:44.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, before you can do that, I'll be blowing the smoke off this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:47.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,The next hole will be through you, not your hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.73,0:06:49.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a foolish man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:01.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you get for belittling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.84,0:07:05.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep well, dear boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.52,0:07:37.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,That was why I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.05,0:07:43.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:46.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,are you guys with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:05.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.89,0:08:07.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the souvenirs for the Big Boss-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.84,0:08:09.87,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave them, our lives come first!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:10.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.21,0:08:13.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I never heard they were this dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:16.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never return to this town again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:22.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,They left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:23.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:28.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, it's fine now, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.40,0:08:32.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that was frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we deceived them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.11,0:08:38.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:44.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all. Now that we've overtaken the mafia from central, our business will boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:47.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,We give and take, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:53.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be compensating us for this little act, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:57.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, Mikhail-san does love to joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.99,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.99,0:09:02.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't joking at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.26,0:09:04.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a world of business, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.96,0:09:07.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I take that debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.20,0:09:12.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you the ones who crushed their car back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:15.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.71,0:09:16.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.09,0:09:19.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:22.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,somebody seems to have crushed their car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.11,0:09:24.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.67,0:09:28.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,there are several spoils of war in mint condition, bought from the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:32.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll sell them off, and split the profits equally with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,That concludes our business here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:39.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,The farce is finally over...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.06,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:48.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,By what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:52.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,You were really getting in to it, Rio-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.87,0:09:54.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,That moonshine,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,if we're discovered, we won't get away with just a court martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:10:00.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,We've infringed on the monopoly and tax law.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.78,0:10:03.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll probably be charged with treason.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:04.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.77,0:10:07.54,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be a side-job that we've inherited from our senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:10.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,but Rio has never once opposed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.10,0:10:12.38,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I was quite surprised too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:22.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was surprised at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:28.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, when I learned that the calvados that my mother loved were made in the fortress...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:37.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it may have been your mother's guidance that brought you to this unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.57,0:10:57.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, off I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:10.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's done. Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks wonderful, Seiya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.18,0:11:21.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.13,0:11:24.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,today is the day for first visits.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.88,0:11:26.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,The priest will be present too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.97,0:11:28.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,So, at least for today-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:29.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:34.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trouble onee-chan, Mishio!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.41,0:11:36.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine to fix your hair, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.26,0:11:38.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.71,0:11:39.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:42.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always fussing about fixing it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.29,0:11:43.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.21,0:11:50.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't do that, Mishio-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:55.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.27,0:12:00.23,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx143.75\fscy111.25\pos(342,272)\frx16\fry4\frz327.487}10 yen 25 sen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.60,0:12:03.00,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,10 yen, 25 sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:07.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey girl, that was dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:11.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry, I was in a daze...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,They are a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:19.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, they got wind of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:25.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.49,0:12:25.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:28.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, Naomi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:30.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:35.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've had money in my wallet to buy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.55,0:12:38.51,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,If I said, "I'll take this now, please", I could buy it, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:44.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if someone snatched up that dolphin, what would you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.59,0:12:48.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone say they wanted it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.36,0:12:50.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no. That was merely an example.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I would...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:53.97,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:13:00.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd tell them that dolphins are scary animals that eat humans, and make them give up on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.30,0:13:04.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:11.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, I'll hold that dolphin until you change your mind. So, rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.94,0:13:16.62,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll just get presents for everyone first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.77,0:13:23.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... father, mother, grandpa and grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.10,0:13:27.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,...and grandpa and grandma in Waren... great grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Granny Nanae who lives next door, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:37.28,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. They're selling so many different things!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.28,0:13:38.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.10,0:13:45.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:47.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you shopping for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.86,0:13:50.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,She's looking for something like a box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:51.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,A box?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:55.02,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you seen anything like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.97,0:13:59.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.46,0:14:04.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're looking for it, want me to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.14,0:14:07.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:11.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here to buy presents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:15.30,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of finding something lovely to send to my family back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.30,0:14:16.79,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I'm not in a hurry, so-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.79,0:14:17.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need help!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.91,0:14:30.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with Mishio-chan...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:37.11,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,T-this is a bit too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:39.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lovely shirt, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.99,0:14:41.77,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,This is cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:41.77,Insert song,,0000,0000,0000,,TL Note: 夜露死苦 - Yoroshiku. Normally means "best regards, please take care of me." But this is written in ateji. It should be read as "slang". Like- Wassup!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.72,0:14:50.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:52.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you happen to see Mishio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:56.96,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,A box?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.96,0:14:59.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She said it was something precious.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:01.82,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:08.65,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,When her mother passed away, all of their household belongings were taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:14.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,It was apparently a memento from her mother that was taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.26,0:15:18.64,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time there's a market in town, she thinks she might find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:24.29,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I said something terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.39,0:15:28.50,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I received a salary for the first time yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,And I said I was sending things back to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:33.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,That is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:39.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I... we are Mishio-san's family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:43.83,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,If she is still envious after all that, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.21,0:15:48.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,...it must be due to my imperfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.05,0:16:05.80,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mama. Which is more important, me or your treasure box?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:07.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.73,0:16:14.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.55,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:33.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,These are Treize's famous firecrackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:41.93,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,They make a powerful sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:42.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,How about some?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.45,0:16:50.14,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.14,0:16:52.21,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina onee-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.21,0:16:53.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:03.68,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,The car!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.08,0:17:12.61,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I'm not Yumina-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:21.10,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina onee-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.43,0:17:23.49,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:24.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.18,0:17:29.78,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.78,0:17:30.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.67,0:17:36.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh! What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:39.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Could... that car...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.36,0:17:42.20,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,...be yours, Naomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.68,0:17:44.24,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,That was you two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:50.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,There's 150 yen in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Compensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.71,0:17:54.56,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:56.88,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Treasure that money, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:59.46,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I got my payment already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.07,0:18:06.48,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Naomi-san... that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:21.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(344,28)}美穂 - beautiful rice {more precisely - beautiful tip of a rice stalk}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.80,0:18:14.66,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,If you carve that on to her seal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.66,0:18:21.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,like fields of abundant rice, her life should filled with happiness too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:22.81,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.31,0:18:27.07,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Miho, it's great that you've received such a fine name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:35.43,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find Mishio-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.40,0:18:42.57,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I was prepared to be her family and heal her heart, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.59,0:18:45.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I am still inexperienced.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.12,0:18:49.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,No, you are doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.45,0:18:54.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:02.32,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad you found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:04.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:07.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an irreplaceable memory of your mother-
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:08.75,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.96,0:19:10.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Here,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.18,0:19:13.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to have it, Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:27.33,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san was taken in by the church when she lost her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:33.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,First, her father was drafted in the army, and never returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.42,0:19:35.03,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,What about her mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.03,0:19:41.01,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mishio-san's family lived on the eastern state border, in the Vingt area.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.52,0:19:42.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:43.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:46.71,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,The town that was attacked by the "invisible death reaper".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:50.36,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,And when the both of them arrived at Seize,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:53.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,her mother had already become ill, and soon after...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.40,0:19:59.09,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.47,0:20:03.08,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,...that she can't fix my hair anymore and she's sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:05.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,And then... and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.84,0:20:10.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,from now on, let the person who treats me most preciously braid it for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:14.98,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yumina, braid my hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:23.15,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans live on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:26.34,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we part with those we hold dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.34,0:20:29.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,...and suffer excruciatingly...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.52,0:20:32.70,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Even then, we live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.70,0:20:34.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,We can live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:39.42,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,That strength is extremely sad, and endearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:45.26,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.60,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.59,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,...Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:02.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's already in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.52,0:21:04.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll go soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.05,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had a hard day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.05,0:21:11.31,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.31,0:21:14.63,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to avoid washing my hair if I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:16.39,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But, things happen, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:19.27,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes, yes! Then, senpai,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.27,0:21:21.44,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,please let me dry your hair off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:23.67,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to touch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.02,0:21:30.95,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't buy the dolphin after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.95,0:21:33.72,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would have bought that as a reward for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.01,0:21:40.53,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-senpai, do you believe in fate?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.53,0:21:42.37,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you bringing that up so suddenly?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:47.91,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Something that happened today made me think about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.91,0:21:50.69,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,That is more than enough of a reward for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:55.58,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:59.84,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate things that are decided and given to you from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:03.92,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,But... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.70,0:22:10.35,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting and being a part of coincidences brought forth by people,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.35,0:22:14.52,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,could possibly change someone's life drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.05,0:22:21.76,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,If you call that fate, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:24.86,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.76,0:22:34.04,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,D-flat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.71,0:22:44.41,Sora no Woto,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you've had a lovely day as well, senpai.
